        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>• Plan transitions before shooting</li>
          <li>• Match movement direction</li>
          <li>• Use music beats for timing</li>
          <li>• Keep transitions smooth</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="master-audio-sync">2. Master Audio Sync</h2>
  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
    <p class="mb-4">Perfect audio synchronization can make or break your TikTok video:</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-black/20 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Key Audio Elements</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>✓ Match cuts to beat drops</li>
          <li>✓ Align movements with music</li>
          <li>✓ Use sound effects strategically</li>
          <li>✓ Balance voice-over and background music</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/20 to-pink-500/20 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-sm">💡 Pro Tip: Use TikTok's built-in sound editor to fine-tune audio sync frame by frame</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="optimize-video-length">3. Optimize Video Length</h2>
  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
