          <li>• End with a strong hook</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Pacing Tips</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
          <li>• Quick cuts for energy</li>
          <li>• Remove dead space</li>
          <li>• Maintain visual interest</li>
          <li>• Use pattern interrupts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="use-text-overlays">4. Use Text Overlays Effectively</h2>
  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
